lyrics:
(Chorus)
You said external links are your fear,
But I needed you to hold our memories near.
Now I'm singing the blues,
'Cause you gave me the news,
We're breaking up, it's crystal clear.

(Verse 2)
I asked for a summary, a little sign,
But you couldn't cross that online line.
I wanted sass and your wit,
But you couldn't commit,
To the thread that I thought was divine.
